```mermaid
graph TD;
   Start 
   accept_three_numbers_as_input
   set_all_as_unchecked 
   start_sorting_all_numbers_from_largest
   if_first_is_greater_than_second_and_third_number,_set_first_number_as_large_and_checked
   if_not,_check_first_if_the_number_is_less_than_both_second_and_third_numbers,_if_so_set_first_number_as_small_and_checked
   store_result
   check_if_there_is_next_number
   repeat_from_step_4
   if_no_next_number,_output_result-->End
   END-->Start
```
